{"tid":255956,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【支付寶打到嚟】香港版明日推出 消費60蚊回贈50","createTime":"2017-05-24T07:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T05:47:16.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e97215a031062e31338fd0dd15ee4969c86dd3a","tid":255956,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170524/large/1495610586_7499.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170524%2Flarge%2F1495610586_7499.png&h=6f2dffff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170524/large/1495610584_9a5d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170524%2Flarge%2F1495610584_9a5d.png&h=2a2d39bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170524/large/1495610582_77d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170524%2Flarge%2F1495610582_77d3.png&h=567e9483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170524/large/1495610589_b932.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170524%2Flarge%2F1495610589_b932.jpg&h=01934eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淘開寶嘅你相信對支付寶唔會陌生，阿里巴巴關聯公司螞蟻金服去年8月獲金管局發出儲值支付工具牌照，終於今日宣佈，明日起正式推出香港版支付寶HK，於App store 及Google Play 上架。<br />\n<br />\n即日起至7月31日的推廣期內，只要在合作商戶消費滿20元以上3次，集齊三個電子印花可獲50元獎賞。另外，推廣期內以中銀信用卡或結餘於淘寶消費，可免手續費，一般信用卡手續費為1.5%。<br />\n<br />\n現時合作商戶包括屈臣氏、百佳、豐澤、美心MX、美心西餅、Starbucks、周大福、I.T.（999）、莎莎（178）、卓悅（653）、海洋公園、一風堂等等。<br />\n<br />\n現時除了可以透過7-11 及OK 便利店充值外，同時可透過渣打銀行（2888）儲值，另外亦可綁定Visa 或Master 信用卡。<br />\n<br />\n螞蟻金服表示，與8大銀行合作，用戶可於銀行提取款項，而支付寶交易方式主要透過掃瞄QR code，未來希望與電訊商合作，提供App 內繳費功能。<br />\n<br />\n記者：梁偉聰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56735893&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56735893%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170524&d=aH8KaMvKRe05vg3cyv5gNmxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=666b4812\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56735893%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170524&h=7547bbe2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56735893&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170524</a>"},{"pid":"c25595c4ac67280e759350bf4d41b72c94db5aef","tid":255956,"uid":4142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"即係咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淘寶一向直接信用卡算"},{"pid":"a9836e570190768c5d4d120e22166bc56f33b400","tid":255956,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淘寶一向直接信用卡算</blockquote><br />\n即係用支付寶HK消費3次有機會比翻$50你囉<br />\nbtw用信用卡好唔抵啊 比佢食手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去7仔OK可以入現金"},{"pid":"2863e45c2543d3a9f2d9269796081f8fbbb52844","tid":255956,"uid":40636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:00:56.000Z","msg":"唔洗實名認證？"},{"pid":"ac2a6b729a1f89b1a9c07cb54ff878b39819b131","tid":255956,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗實名認證？</blockquote><br />\n正路都要啦<br />\n<br />\n你睇番 tap &amp; go , payme, 果D全部電子錢包都要實名"},{"pid":"ebbda7cab797370eb6a12328e3dd78a335fea460","tid":255956,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T